
===================================
📌 1. Finglish Version (Persian Latin Script)
===================================

📖 **Tashrih:**
    Dastoor `gp-archive` baraye poshtiban-giri (backup) va bargardandan-e (restore) etela'at Google Play estefade mishavad. In dastoor be shoma komak mikonad ta az barname-ha (apps), bazi-ha (games), va etela'at hesab-e Google Play khod poshtiban begirid va dar sorat-e niaz, anha ra bargardanid.

⚙️ **Gozine-ha:**
    🔹 `gp-archive backup`  --> 💾 Az hameye barname-ha va bazi-ha poshtiban migirad.
    🔹 `gp-archive restore` --> 📤 Etela'at poshtiban-giri shode ra bargardandan.
    🔹 `gp-archive list`    --> 📝 List-e poshtiban-giri haye mojood ra namayesh midahad.
    🔹 `gp-archive --help` --> ❓ Komak va rahnamara namayesh midahad.

🛠 **Mesal-ha:**

    $ gp-archive backup

    🔹 Az hameye barname-ha va bazi-ha poshtiban migirad.

    $ gp-archive restore

    🔹 Akharin poshtiban-giri ra bargardandan.

    $ gp-archive list

    🔹 List-e poshtiban-giri haye mojood ra dar file haye archive namayesh midahad.

✅ **Mesal sade:**

    $ gp-archive backup --output ~/backup_gp_archive.tar.gz

    🔹 Az hameye barname-ha va bazi-ha poshtiban migirad va dar file-e `backup_gp_archive.tar.gz` dar pooshe-ye home zakhire mikonad.

===================================
📌 2. English Version
===================================

📖 **Description:**
    The `gp-archive` command is used for backing up and restoring Google Play data. It helps you backup and restore your apps, games, and Google Play account data.

⚙️ **Options:**
    🔹 `gp-archive backup`  --> 💾 Backup all apps and games.
    🔹 `gp-archive restore` --> 📤 Restore previously backed up data.
    🔹 `gp-archive list`    --> 📝 List available backups.
    🔹 `gp-archive --help` --> ❓ Display help and usage information.

🛠 **Examples:**

    $ gp-archive backup

    🔹 Backup all apps and games.

    $ gp-archive restore

    🔹 Restore the latest backup.

    $ gp-archive list

    🔹 List available backups stored in archive files.

✅ **Simple Example:**

    $ gp-archive backup --output ~/backup_gp_archive.tar.gz

    🔹 Backup all apps and games and save them to the `backup_gp_archive.tar.gz` file in the home directory.
